description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SAVE THE DATE: Thursday 12&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;th&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; November at 10.00 am&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will be holding our first virtual nursing recruitment day at Epsom &amp; St. Helier University Hospitals NHS Trust on Thursday 12th November! If you are interested in hearing about the job opportunities we have to offer, meet some of our clinical teams, learn more about the trust and how we can support your career - &lt;strong&gt;PLEASE JOIN US VIA THE LINK IN THE JOB DESCRIPTION. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At the open day we are will be introducing our some of our departments, telling you about our exciting plans for our brand new acute hospital, showing you how our team pulled together to support each other during COVID and detailing some of the opportunities available to Epsom &amp; St Helier Trust staff including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* access to our quality marked CapitalNurse preceptorship programme for newly qualified nurses&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* support from our clinical practice educators/facilitators&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* support with applications for post-registration courses to allow you to follow your career pathway&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* access to progression courses and nationally run leadership programmes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At ESTH we are committed to acknowledging and building on our successes to ensure we give the best care we can to our patients every day. Our staff wanted more than a set of tools to help support them to do this - they wanted a cultural way of doing things here at ESTH. We have therefore recently launched IDEAS, which is our unique QI programme at Epsom and St Helier.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful candidates will have a genuine desire to become a part of our amazing team and provide outstanding care for our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So if you’re the kind of person who cares about getting things right and wants to make a difference in a forward thinking team we would love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note – if you wish to be interviewed please apply on line and we will contact you to arrange virtual interviews. If you are interested in working with us, apply today.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
